### ================================================================
### Healthcare Backend API — REST Client (VS Code)
### 확장: REST Client (Huachao Mao) 설치 필요
### ================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

# ① 로그인 후 응답 토큰을 아래에 붙여넣기
@accessToken  = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
@patientId    = user_001


### ================================================================
### 1. 인증 (Auth)
### ================================================================

### 1-1. 로그인 — 의사 (DOCT)
# @name loginDoctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "admin",
  "passwd": "admin001123!"
}

###

### 1-2. 로그인 — 환자 (PATI)
# @name loginPatient
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "user_001",
  "passwd": "user_001123!"
}

###

### 1-3. AccessToken 재발급
# RefreshToken 은 JWT_REFRESH_SECRET으로 서명됨 — AccessToken으로 대체 불가
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### 1-4. 로그인 실패 — 잘못된 비밀번호 (401 예상)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "user_001",
  "passwd": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 1-5. AccessToken을 RefreshToken 자리에 (401 예상 — 키 분리 검증)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{accessToken}}"
}

###


### ================================================================
### 2. 회원 (Members)
### ================================================================

### 2-1. 회원 목록 — 전체
GET {{baseUrl}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 2-2. 회원 목록 — 이름 검색
GET {{baseUrl}}/members?search=김
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 2-3. 회원 목록 — 유형 필터
GET {{baseUrl}}/members?member_type=PATI
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 2-4. 회원 상세 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 2-5. 최근 건강 데이터 조회 (실시간 초기 로딩)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health/latest?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 2-6. 건강 데이터 기간 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{patientId}}/health?from=2026-07-12T00:00:00%2B09:00&to=2026-07-19T23:59:59%2B09:00
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###


### ================================================================
### 3. 채팅 (AI Agent 프록시)
### ================================================================

### 3-1. AI 채팅
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "message": "최근 혈당이 높은데 식이요법을 알려줘",
  "member_id": "{{patientId}}"
}

###


### ================================================================
### 4. 알림 (Slack Webhook)
### ================================================================

### 4-1. Slack 수동 메시지 전송
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook/slack
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "message": "[테스트] REST Client 수동 알림 메시지"
}

###


### ================================================================
### 5. 인증 오류 케이스
### ================================================================

### 5-1. 토큰 없이 요청 (401 예상)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members

###

### 5-2. 잘못된 토큰 (401 예상)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###
